{"tid":231802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有d巴士司機係的確好賤。","createTime":"2017-05-06T10:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T14:35:09.000Z","uid":85524,"like":14,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0b1ab73721bb519474059753b61fdbdac19abee","tid":231802,"uid":85524,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T10:14:16.000Z","msg":"我知咁講可能會惹起不少人說不要太敏感果d,  事關都網上search過唔少post有d人遇巴士司機見到佢就黎追到車時，個司機就立刻關門走佬。<br />\n<br />\n我頭先遇到既係， 我本來有d意外， 要用拐杖行過去巴士站， 個司機企左係站到望風景， 我慢慢行到去佢身旁，一開口想問路： &quot;唔該。。司。。&quot;<br />\n條友即刻標上去巴士到，關埋門， 我都O左咀， 唔洗咁ma... 但我又冇嬲到， 只覺感慨， 唔係連香港都變成咁掛？<br />\n之後慢慢行去車尾影底個車牌嚇下佢， 都冇諗住投訴佢，見佢個樣都怯怯地。<br />\n<br />\n以前都試過一兩次追巴士， 真係睇準時機就到果刻就關門， 同賤精先生果幕關lift真係有d似。 唔明 d巴士司機點解咁做， 咁做會心理平衡定點呢， 咁搞笑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3rwyz06l\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3rwyz06l&h=83fcd3bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f65612dc55ae1f2e1dd038c2e5342254748ba07a","tid":231802,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T10:14:30.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9b54499d89e05bfb7cef8050ad9d7e7faf06b23a","tid":231802,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T10:15:44.000Z","msg":"你明明就好嬲點解要扮無所謂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6e5b7e18d1fb842b29f140d1d9f4a53d356752","tid":231802,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T10:16:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm</blockquote><br />\n自己開post自己留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6e01bc06e56353478fc227aacca56d526dc524","tid":231802,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T10:16:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>lm</blockquote><br />\n自己開post自己留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為lihkg唔lm唉知點揾番自己post"},{"pid":"5e9089